This is a "plugin" for the Video Disk Recorder (VDR).

Written by:                  Sundararaj <sundararaj.reel@googlemail.com>

Project's homepage:          URL

Latest version available at: URL

See the file COPYING for license information.

Description:
    This plugin gets EPG data from internet (currently only from bleb.org) and loads it into VDR.

One should be able to Enable/Disable parts of the plugin or manually start download(Setup->System settings->Xmlepg2vdr).
Currently, download from internet alone is implemented.

Also see HISTORY, URLREADME
